00:02:49.272 --> 00:02:50.230 align:middle line:90%
death and resurrection.

00:02:50.230 --> 00:02:52.690 align:middle line:84%
>> Death and resurrection,
you find in--

00:02:52.690 --> 00:02:54.760 align:middle line:84%
well, a great
percentage of the myths,

00:02:54.760 --> 00:02:57.340 align:middle line:84%
