00:04:01.310 --> 00:04:03.438 align:middle line:90%
He calls us into our greatness.

00:04:03.438 --> 00:04:05.980 align:middle line:84%
>> As if he is a template for
what the human race can become.

00:04:05.980 --> 00:04:07.150 align:middle line:90%
>> Exactly, wonderful.

00:04:07.150 --> 00:04:11.210 align:middle line:84%
Yes, he is a pattern of
possibility, the higher man,

00:04:11.210 --> 00:04:12.010 align:middle line:90%
you see?

00:04:12.010 --> 00:04:14.020 align:middle line:84%
