reality probably was, you know?

00:04:37.030 --> 00:04:38.860 align:middle line:84%
You look at
psychologically, the way

00:04:38.860 --> 00:04:41.950 align:middle line:84%
he relates with
such leaky margins,

00:04:41.950 --> 00:04:44.020 align:middle line:84%
with such empathy to
everyone he meets,

00:04:44.020 --> 00:04:46.150 align:middle line:84%
his deep appreciation
of children,

00:04:46.150 --> 00:04:49.540 align:middle line:84%
his calling forth of children,
the little child shall lead us.

00:04:49.540 --> 00:04:52.063 align:middle line:84%
