looking for the Messiah.

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:14.620 align:middle line:84%
And some claimed
to be the Messiah.

00:05:14.620 --> 00:05:16.690 align:middle line:84%
And what was unique
about him is here

00:05:16.690 --> 00:05:19.390 align:middle line:84%
you had the great tale of the
mystery, the dying and rising

00:05:19.390 --> 00:05:22.330 align:middle line:84%
God, which of course, was
one of the great stories

00:05:22.330 --> 00:05:24.550 align:middle line:84%
and celebrations in
the ancient world.

00:05:24.550 --> 00:05:27.170 align:middle line:84%
