who actually did it.

00:05:27.170 --> 00:05:29.080 align:middle line:84%
So this is the nature
of the cross, you know?

00:05:29.080 --> 00:05:31.150 align:middle line:84%
Here's a Jewish
political tragedy,

00:05:31.150 --> 00:05:34.240 align:middle line:84%
and here is the great mystery
of death and Resurrection.

00:05:34.240 --> 00:05:39.820 align:middle line:84%
