of human capacity

00:05:42.130 --> 00:05:44.890 align:middle line:84%
and knows that I and
my Father are one,

00:05:44.890 --> 00:05:47.680 align:middle line:84%
that we are all children
of God, that we are all--

00:05:47.680 --> 00:05:50.140 align:middle line:84%
we are all part of
the divine parentage.

00:05:50.140 --> 00:05:53.710 align:middle line:84%
