00:07:07.330 --> 00:07:11.920 align:middle line:84%
He's really the man for all
seasons and for all eras,

00:07:11.920 --> 00:07:12.720 align:middle line:90%
you know?

00:07:12.720 --> 00:07:14.303 align:middle line:84%
Right now, there's
a tremendous spread

00:07:14.303 --> 00:07:16.760 align:middle line:84%
