orchestration of realities.

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:35.680 align:middle line:90%
You can make things grow.

00:07:35.680 --> 00:07:36.550 align:middle line:90%
You can heal.

00:07:36.550 --> 00:07:37.350 align:middle line:90%
You can.

00:07:37.350 --> 00:07:39.070 align:middle line:90%
And he keeps saying, you can.

00:07:39.070 --> 00:07:41.800 align:middle line:84%
Don't just look at
me, look at what

00:07:41.800 --> 00:07:44.500 align:middle line:84%
I am reflecting what you are
